import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import {PropsTable, Playground} from 'docz';
import ImageFrame from '../src/core-ui/ImageFrame';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"imageframe"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#imageframe"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`ImageFrame`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#properties"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={ImageFrame} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Basic Usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<ImageFrame
  imageUri="https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/r/334x484/images/anime/1173/92110.jpg?s=9055f67e52d09a3f331b686f02efa37e"
  title="Shingeki no Kyojin Season 3"
/>`} __scope={{props,ImageFrame}}>
  <ImageFrame 
    imageUri="https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/r/334x484/images/anime/1173/92110.jpg?s=9055f67e52d09a3f331b686f02efa37e"
    title="Shingeki no Kyojin Season 3"
  />
</Playground></MDXTag>
